# Explorations

- Register explorers in `explorations/registry.tsx`; lessons reference `explorationId`.
- Reuse `MafsSceneShell`, `ParameterControls`, `ExplorationToggles`, `PresetPicker`, `SceneReadout`, `ResetButton`.
- Seed from `src/lessons/exampleData.ts` / shared example ids (same matrices as the guided scene for that lesson).
- Prefer progressive disclosure (`<details>`) for advanced controls; keep the first view focused.
- Role colors via CSS variables (`--role-*`); keep legend swatches in sync with drawn vectors.
- Colocate explorer CSS next to the component; match existing naming.
